{"tid":2214633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"課程檢討報告︱教局不想學生「追新聞」 資深通識教師反駁：課程列明可多用時事新資訊","createTime":"2020-09-23T11:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T12:32:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"510433847ba971ed7a2962d21e0bd3264f8c45f8","tid":2214633,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"學校課程檢討專責小組昨向教育局提交報告，提出多項有關通識科富爭議性建議，惟教育局未按慣例召開記者會，僅安排4間傳媒「小圍」採訪小組主席陳黃麗娟等人。陳太受訪時表示，不希望師生每日每周「追新聞」和添加資料，令學生要「沒完沒了討論」。有資深通識科教師駁斥，課程指引列明「時事的最新資訊可以多加採用」，若不討論，令學生與科目的距離拉遠。他又指，教師「唔係追新聞」，只會挑選與課程相關內容與學生討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/ZVJ2FCYCMFETHA7LE6QWVJ43FY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FZVJ2FCYCMFETHA7LE6QWVJ43FY%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9reFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=d49d2d45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FZVJ2FCYCMFETHA7LE6QWVJ43FY%2F&h=e55b8430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/ZVJ2FCYCMFETHA7LE6QWVJ43FY/</a>"},{"pid":"657f33d9a3811c0244961441ea95b2161df41499","tid":2214633,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"唔比人睇新聞咁不如叫人背習語錄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39244168aa48aa92204d316600db9f23b69b26a","tid":2214633,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}